"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-06-15-australia-swimming-trials-final-day-olympics-campbell-simpson-103982450\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  Sport  Topic:Swimming  Cate Campbell swam the 50m freestyle 24 hours after the crushing disappointment of missing out on the 100m final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cate Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(AAP Image: Dave Hunt)  After all the emotion of Friday's 100-metre freestyle, Cate Campbell was back in action in Saturday's 50m free.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Hunt_(Christian_apologist)\", \"score\": 0.43234871504388145, \"rank\": 0.611764705882408, \"text\": \"Dave Hunt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Hunt_(Christian_apologist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Hunt_(Christian_apologist)\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cate Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cate_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Campbell's final chance.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999176907, \"rank\": 8.243683823883699e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How difficult must it be to pick yourself up after enduring the sort of disappointment that one must fear in the deepest recesses of your soul, having been ill coming into what could be the final event of her career.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A soul-testing 24 hours later, Campbell was back.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999176907, \"rank\": 8.243683823883699e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Facing another test.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A final test.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A test she passed.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To get into the final would have required a sub-25-second swim, and Campbell was one of seven swimmers who managed that, edging out Mollie O'Callaghan with a time of 24.85.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999176907, \"rank\": 8.243683823883699e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell looked slightly slow off the blocks, but powered down the first 40m of the Brisbane Aquatic Centre pool, before fading slightly in the final 10m.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999176907, \"rank\": 8.243683823883699e-11, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9974261455453639, \"rank\": 0.002533484541911861, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, it was enough to get her into the evening's final as the sixth-fastest qualifier.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shayna Jack qualified fastest in the morning for the 50m freestyle final.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shayna Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Quinn Rooney)  Shayna Jack clocked the fastest time of the heats, swimming a speedy 24.02 after the emotion of qualifying for her first Olympics in Friday night's 100m.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shayna Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayna_Jack\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not get very much sleep last night,\\\" Jack said.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9521488501455354, \"rank\": 0.05016051683674683, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just really wanted to wind down and continue my focus.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will definitely spend time after tonight acknowledging what I have been through and what I have done this week and let myself feel that excitement.\\\"\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack qualified ahead of Meg Harris (24.47), Bronte Campbell (24.56), reigning Olympic champion Emma McKeon (24.72) and Olivia Wunsch (24.73).\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1750, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9521488501455354, \"rank\": 0.05016051683674683, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meg Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Harris\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bronte Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bronte_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma McKeon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_McKeon\"}, {\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\", \"score\": 0.9999883470046854, \"rank\": 1.1653131030904881e-05, \"text\": \"Olivia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Dunham\"}, {\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Wunsch\", \"score\": 0.9999999989081516, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wunsch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Wunsch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Wunsch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alexandria Perkins was the final qualifier in 25.02.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Safe-Zone\", \"score\": 0.8166031703200437, \"rank\": 0.2245850039620996, \"text\": \"Alexandria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Safe-Zone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria_Safe-Zone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC Sportis live blogging every day of the Paris Olympics  ABC Sportis live blogging every day of the Paris Olympics  Cody Simpson earned his spot on the 2022 Commonwealth Games team.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999573567335854, \"rank\": 4.2645084993378007e-05, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999573567335854, \"rank\": 4.2645084993378007e-05, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cody Simpson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Quinn Rooney)  Earlier in the week, coach Michael Bohl said it was always going to be a big ask for pop-star Cody Simpson to make the squad for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Bohl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Bohl\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Bohl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Bohl\"}, {\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cody Simpson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The reality is you gotta go off rankings,\\\" Bohl said.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's about fourth or fifth or sixth in the 100 fly \\u2026 for him to make this team it's going to be a huge sum.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's possible, but it's expected that it's gonna be a challenge for him to do it.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not saying he's gonna make it.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not saying he's not gonna make it.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got as good a chance as anyone else.\\\"\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simpson's chances were enhanced slightly by the withdrawal of Kyle Chalmers from the heats, and he took that chance, swimming an impressive 51.78 to win his heat by a body-length and qualify fifth-fastest for the final.\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyle Chalmers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Chalmers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cody Simpson made the final of the 100m butterfly.\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2899, \"end\": 2911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cody Simpson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Delly Carr)  Chalmers,who revealed he was suffering a back injury after qualifying in the 100m freestyle, could not risk further injury having already made the team.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC Sport Daily is your daily sports conversation.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3127, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"score\": 0.9997636331630049, \"rank\": 0.00023642271949992548, \"text\": \"ABC Sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We dive into the biggest story of the day and get you up to speed with everything else that's making headlines.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian record holder Matthew Temple led home the qualifiers with a 51.46, just outside the standard of 51.17, with Ben Armbruster second.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3291, \"end\": 3301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999828775063898, \"rank\": 1.685207713475932e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 3316, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Temple_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9999849671591969, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Temple\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Temple_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Temple_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bohl said that, whether or not Simpson made the final cut to travel to Paris was irrelevant and that he had already achieved what he set out to do.\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3505, \"end\": 3510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.428963312099152e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's rather nice and, you know, we are hoping that he can get up and just get the best out of himself.\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I think, what he did in making that Commonwealth Games team is what he set out to achieve.\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3729, \"end\": 3747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999455211734156, \"rank\": 3.393188737871866e-05, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted to make an Australian team.\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9946143633525443, \"rank\": 0.005414761483122806, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not that he does not make this one.\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He desperately wants to make this.\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, you know, making that Australian team was a win for him.\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3924, \"end\": 3939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9946143633525443, \"rank\": 0.005414761483122806, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being out of the sport for a long number of years and coming back and getting in is just testament to his willpower.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just been great.\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all very, very proud of him and the group.\\\"\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LIVE  LIVE  Topic:Golf  Topic:Golf  Analysis by Dean Bilton  Topic:Heatwaves  Topic:World Politics  Analysis by David Taylor  Topic:World Politics  Topic:US Elections  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Topic:Swimming  Brisbane  Olympic Games  Sport  Swimming  Topic:Heatwaves  Topic:World Politics  Analysis by David Taylor  Topic:World Politics  Topic:US Elections  Topic:Wildlife Traffic Accidents and Incidents  Topic:Golf  LIVE  Topic:Arson  We acknowledge Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples as the First Australians and Traditional Custodians of the lands where we live, learn, and work.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4202, \"end\": 4206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.922431435403316e-14, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 4207, \"end\": 4213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bilton-in-Ainsty\", \"score\": 0.9968332283372373, \"rank\": 0.0015912268622433727, \"text\": \"Bilton\", \"types\": [\"Q4869